text: Prosopocera cylindrica is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Per Olof Christopher Aurivillius in 1903. It is known from the Democratic Republic of the Congo and Cameroon.BioLib.cz - Prosopocera cylindrica.
